%section.main-content
  %h1 Standard Notes Pro
  %p Standard Notes Pro is a paid membership that allows members to access exclusive benefits and premium extensions, and helps Standard Notes survive and sustain for the long run.
  %p.bold Benefits:
  %ul
    %li
      Access to all Pro extensions, current and future.
      %a{"ui-sref" => "extensions"} (See full list here)
    %li
      Support Standard Note's mission for privacy and longevity. In return, you'll get a permanent mention on our homepage in the Credits section, as well as on the
      %a{"ui-sref" => "producers"} Producer's page.
    %li Priority support, including 1-on-1 technical assistance with setting up your own Standard Notes/Standard File server (for maximum privacy).

  %h2.inline.mr-20 $30/year
  %button.black.inline{"ng-click" => "formData.showEmailForm = true", "ng-if" => "!formData.showEmailForm"} Subscribe
  .mt-10{"ng-if" => "formData.showEmailForm"}
    %input.form-control.inline.top{"type" => "email", "ng-model" => "formData.email", "placeholder" => "Enter your email address", "style" => "height: 39px;"}
    %button.black.inline.top{"ng-click" => "submitEmail()"} Continue

  .mt-10{"ng-if" => "formData.processing"} Processing...
  .mt-10.bold{"ng-if" => "formData.success"} Success! Welcome to Standard Notes Pro. Redirecting...
  .mt-10.red{"ng-if" => "formData.error"} {{formData.error.message}}
  .mt-10{"ng-if" => "formData.registrationResponse"} {{formData.registrationResponse}}

  %p
    %em Credit cards and Bitcoin accepted. Powered by Stripe.
